# This dataset contains laptop listings scraped from Flipkart, one of India’s largest e-commerce platforms.
It includes 936 laptops across multiple brands, collected from the first 10 pages of search results for “laptops under 1 lakh”.

--> The goal of this dataset is to provide clean, structured, analysis-ready data for:

- Price comparison

- Laptop specifications analysis

- Trend insights

- Machine learning prediction tasks

- E-commerce research

# The dataset has been fully cleaned #
 ✔ Prices converted to numeric
 ✔ Ratings & reviews split
 ✔ Storage, display size, warranty, OS cleaned
 ✔ Company extracted automatically
 ✔ Suitable for ML/EDA
